metadata.name: Fall #1/10
metadata.description:
This is an image of waterfall we found after a small trek near Vythiri Resort in Wayanad, Kerala, India.

It was not an expansive place, so used the 1:1 crop to give the cramped space feel.

Fall colours is not common for us. A red leaf amidst green & earthy location compelled me take this striking image by juxtaposing the fall colour leaf against a (water)fall
